    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of reliability and comfort. It has been meticulously cared for, with a consistent maintenance schedule that ensures the engine and transmission operate smoothly. The exterior retains a deep luster, showing only the minor road nicks one would expect from a car that has been driven with pride. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the upholstery is firm and free of tears, and every electronic feature\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions perfectly. With a set of high-tread tires and a recent multi-point inspection already completed, this car is ready for the road today without any immediate needs.",
      "price": 32500.0,
