      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies reliability and sophisticated design. This unit has undergone a comprehensive inspection to ensure it meets our standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Featuring a consistent service history and a well-preserved interior, it offers a premium driving experience at an exceptional value. We invite discerning buyers to experience the quality and performance of this distinguished model firsthand.",
