    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable daily driver that still looks great on the road! I've taken good care of it, and it's totally ready to hit the pavement with a new owner today. It's got plenty of life left in it and runs like a champ. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
