    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit features a linear power band and exceptional throttle response thanks to its individual throttle bodies and high compression ratio. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, and the chassis remains composed through corners aided by a factory M-variable differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been performed, including a comprehensive double-VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate common floor pan fatigue. The suspension geometry is tight, benefiting from refreshed bushings and dampers. While the exterior shows the honest patina of a weekend tourer, the drivetrain and cooling system are optimized for performance longevity.",
